<HEAD>Arkansas Governor To Announce Dukakis Endorsement</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ORLANDO, Fla. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Arkansas Gov. Bill Clinton says he will
endorse Massachusetts Gov. Miicheal Dukakis for the Democratic
nomination for president today but denies he has any interest in
the vice presidential nomination.
   ``Dukakis needs a Southern senator as a running mate, not
