<HEAD>Sikh Family of Seven, Six Others Killed by Extremists</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW DELHI, India (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Sikh extremists shot to death a family
of seven and then killed a blind man and another person while
