<HEAD>Name Of Slain Beirut Hostage Added To Memorial Plaques</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The State Department on Friday added two
names, including that of slain Beirut hostage William Buckley, to
memorial plaques for the more than 200 American officials killed in
the line of diplomatic duty since 1780.
   In a ceremony attended by several hundred present and former
